            "about": "a submarine signal intermittently bathes a steel corridor\nthe paper reveals something in the amber glow different from what you remember\nanother pattern is on the wall now, but what was in your glass last night? you look again\nthe room feels slightly smaller than before\nyou look again\nanother pattern is on the wall now, in the intermittent amber glow it looks again at your glass\nyou look down at the paper\na submarine corridor bathed in amber red\nyou look again\nnow a dark room has paper hanging on strings\na faint siren is heard\nyou look down into the corridor\nyou look again\n深淵0006",
