            "about": "Recordings of Tokyo game centers in April 2023 using a stealth binaural microphone setup. Headphones recommended!\nI visited tokyo in April 2023 partly fueled by a vehement infatuation with shooting games, a.k.a shoot 'em ups, or \"shmups\", and I needed to see them in their original state, occupying rows of cabinets with glowing screens. My intense fascination with the games was only heightened by the physical experience. I'd played them at home, sure, but it was nothing like \"the real thing\". Of course this was for pleasure but the stakes were raised - my time, my money, my sanity. Players lined the halls, some remaining locked into their singular manic obsession, some merely passing by. Who triumphs? Who falls? The cacophony of the game center is the great equaliser.\nA0011",
            "credits": "released September 20, 2024",
            "license": "all rights reserved",
