            "datePublished": "10 Feb 2021 00:00:00 GMT",
            "about": "Dual compositions of tactile recordings, field recordings, and electronics.\nOr in the words of the artist themselves:\n\"Side A \"an instant folded over itself into a knot\" uses minutiae of everyday sounds expanded and conjoined spatially and temporally to invert the paradigm of proximity.\nSide B \"ridges protruding from a surface\" is a blind exploration of textures that lie out of earshot, revealing straight lines and blurred patches that protrude from the featureless, yet tangible silence that surrounds us.\"\n深淵0004",
